Show HN: Business Observability Platform (Pagerduty for Operations)
text:
Hello everyone!

For the past 3 years of working with business teams, we saw that things break everyday & they are constantly firefighting. We have built a solution that helps them become proactive through real time monitoring, alerting and issue response (similar to what devops teams have in tools like Datadog, Pagerduty and Opsgenie).

You can write rules on SQL, assign them to people, set up escalations and resolve through whatsapp, slack & teams. Please check this out and do drop your feedback. Would mean a lot to us!

Link: https://go.locale.ai/signup
